    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion </strong>and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 2,
