    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>halved broccoli </strong>to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 4-5 min or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> then add to a colander</p><p>Once tender, drain the <strong>broccoli</strong> over the spinach so that it starts to wilt – this is your <strong>cooked spinach & broccoli</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
