    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cooked spinach </strong>and<strong> broccoli stems </strong>(save the florets for later!)<strong> </strong>to a<strong> food processor </strong>with your <strong>basil</strong> and the <strong>remaining chopped garlic</strong></p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>and blitz until smooth – this is your<strong> green veg sauce</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of water if it's looking a little dry!</p>",
