    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the risotto is cooked through, add the <strong>green veg sauce </strong>to the pan with your <strong>soft cheese</strong>, <strong>broccoli florets </strong>and a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min – this is your <strong>green veg-packed risotto</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p><p>Break the <strong>black</strong> <strong>sesame cheese crisp</strong> into shards</p>",
